snippet.title: Legends of Kingdom Rush Official trailer
snippet.description:
Pick your favorite Legend and choose your companions wisely, your adventure is about to begin! We are thrilled to announce that Legends of Kingdom Rush will be available for steam ! 
Legendary heroes, amazing companions, new adventures, new achievements, new lore!
Add Legends of Kingdom Rush to your steam Wishlist NOW http https://bit.ly/3OLfplu
Find it also on AppleArcade
